column5: If anyone's ass deserves a beating it's satan. That motherfucker is going down.
Nah I will never convert to the marijuana cult that is taking over.
Not putting someone else's shit inside me sorry. Unless they can put it inside a capsule which can be taken orally with orange juice and I can pretend it's just another probiotic then forget it.

Spot on, our culture despises those who are considered weak or inferior. Better to die with honor and some dignity than a slow miserable death with others giving you shit for still existing. I have ME/CFS so I know this all too well trust me. My brother was killed instantly on his motorcycle at age 21 and he had hundreds at his funeral and to this day is seen as a great young man. There isn't a day that goes by I wouldn't gladly trade places with him. He loved life and lived it to the fullest and gets taken away, I hate this world and am forced to stay. Now that's fucked up.
